title: Serendipity Foods
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Dishes such as roasted vegetables, salads, jacket potatoes with beans, chips, and hummus. Has soy milkshakes when requested. Prices are slightly higher than other area cafes. Staff is knowledgeable about allergens and is accommodating to vegans.
